transcripts.transcript_text: Speaker A: The vodafone voicemail service 407-469-8596.

Speaker B: Hello?
Speaker A: Hello?
Speaker B: Hi.
Speaker A: Yeah, hello. Actually calling you from Ambit. Am I speaking as Natalie here?
Speaker B: Yeah, that's correct.
Speaker A: Natalie, I just talked to the property team. They have told me that they will be giving you a reply about the viewing and the contract by today. They have also taken you taken your contact details. So they will be connecting you very shortly and getting this done in their.
Speaker B: Okay, perfect. Wonderful. Thank you so much.
Speaker A: You're welcome. If you need anything, just drop me a WhatsApp message. You do have all the details. You can just let me know if there is something needed.
Speaker B: Okay, perfect. Thank you so much.
Speaker A: You're welcome. Have a great day. Bye Bye.

Speaker B: Bye.

Speaker B: Hello.
Speaker A: Yeah, hello, Natalie from Amber.
Speaker B: Oh, hi. Hello.
Speaker A: Hi, Natalie. How are you?
Speaker B: I'm good, thank you. How are you?
Speaker A: I'm also good, thank you for asking. Natalie. Just wanted to confirm if the property has provided you a viewing.
Speaker B: No, they haven't. I've been. I've been. They did call me though and they said they're going to sort it out and then I didn't end up getting. Getting a response back. So then I emailed them again and still nothing.
Speaker A: I think that this must be because of the move in since they have to move in place alongside now, so they are a bit busy. Although it will be done by Monday since it's a weekend like today and.
Speaker B: Tomorrow, it will.
Speaker A: Be done by Monday. I will try to get this all completed by Monday and also arrange the video.
Speaker B: Okay, thank you so much. Thank you.
Speaker A: And when would you like to move in Mahathli?
Speaker B: As soon as possible. Really?
Speaker A: Got it. And I'll sort this out by Monday and then you can move in by Tuesday or Wednesday accordingly.
Speaker B: Okay, lovely. Thank you so much.
Speaker A: You're welcome. Have a great day. Bye.
Speaker B: Bye. Thank you. You too. Have a good day. Bye.
